column2: select top # p.objID, p.ra, p.dec,  p.petroMag_u-extinction_u AS mag_u,  p.petroMag_g-extinction_g AS mag_g, p.petroMag_r-extinction_r AS mag_r, p.petroMag_i-extinction_i AS mag_i, p.petroMag_z-extinction_z AS mag_z, p.petroR5#_r, p.deVRad_r, s.z AS RedShift from photoObj AS p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID where s.class = &&& and p.ObjID<># and s.z># and s.zWarning = # ORDER BY s.z
